</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>copy</code></strong> イベントは、ユーザーがブラウザーのユーザーインターフェイスからコピー操作を行おうとした時に発行されます。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"構文","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<p>このイベント名を <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\" title=\"addEventListener()\"><code>addEventListener()</code></a> のようなメソッドで使用するか、イベントハンドラープロパティを設定するかしてください。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'copy'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function-variable function\">oncopy</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"イベント型","title":"イベント型","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ClipboardEvent\"><code>ClipboardEvent</code></a> です。 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a> を継承しています。</p><svg viewBox=\"-1 -1 650 42\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMinYMin meet\">\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\">\n    <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"75\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#fff\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"37.5\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      Event\n    </text>\n  </a>\n  <line x1=\"75\" y1=\"14\" x2=\"105\" y2=\"14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" \"=\"\"></line>\n  <polyline points=\"75,14 85,9 85,19 75,14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" fill=\"#fff\"></polyline>\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ClipboardEvent\">\n    <rect x=\"105\" y=\"0\" width=\"112\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#F4F7F8\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"161\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      ClipboardEvent\n    </text>\n  </a></svg>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"イベントプロパティ","title":"イベントプロパティ","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>親である <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a> から継承したプロパティもあります。</em></p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"clipboardevent.clipboarddata\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ClipboardEvent/clipboardData\"><code>ClipboardEvent.clipboardData</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer\"><code>DataTransfer</code></a> オブジェクトで、ユーザーが行った <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/cut_event\" title=\"cut\"><code>cut</code></a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/copy_event\" title=\"copy\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>copy</code></a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/paste_event\" title=\"paste\"><code>paste</code></a> 操作によって影響されたデータと MIME タイプが入ります。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>この例では、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a> からのすべてのコピーと貼り付けをブロックします。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>このテキストエリアで実行してみる<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>textarea</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>editor<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">rows</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>3<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>このフィールドにテキストをコピー＆ペーストしてみてください。<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>textarea</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>ログ:<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>log<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"javascript","title":"JavaScript","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-